Privacy Policy for Color Dash App

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Color Dash collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users (hereinafter referred to as "Users") of the Color Dash mobile application (hereinafter referred to as the "App").

Personal Identification Information

Color Dash does not collect any personal identification information from Users. The App is designed to be a simple game without the need for creating accounts, providing personal information, or collecting any sensitive data.

Non-personal Identification Information

The App may collect non-personal identification information about Users whenever they interact with the App. This information may include the type of device used, the device's unique identifier, the operating system, and other technical information.

How We Use Collected Information

Color Dash does not collect any personally identifiable information from Users. The non-personal identification information collected is used solely for the purpose of enhancing the User experience and improving the performance of the App.

Third-Party Services

Color Dash does not utilize any third-party services, such as analytics providers or advertising networks, that may collect information from Users.

Data Security

Color Dash takes appropriate measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of any non-personal identification information collected.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

Color Dash may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Users are encouraged to frequently check this page for any changes. You acknowledge and agree that it is your responsibility to review this Privacy Policy periodically and become aware of modifications.

Your Acceptance of These Terms

By using the Color Dash App, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use the App.

Contacting Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the practices of the Color Dash App, please contact us at whenuwakeupsunwill@gmail.com.
